This is a tough spot. Bob's offering $1,450,000 and is saying he won't go any higher. He is also saying that his alternative is an offer of $1,500,000. My minimum acceptable price is $1,500,000. If I reject, I risk losing the deal entirely and getting nothing, or getting Bob to say "I'm going with John".

It seems unlikely that I will be able to get a price above $1,500,000 since he is willing to pay that to John. I should sell to John to get $1,500,000.

{"decision": "SellToJhon"}
